{"tid":1159169,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華員會：要求胡志偉就斥責特首言論公開道歉","createTime":"2019-05-17T12:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T22:45:57.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"124c4382d6749a372ac03e3a1a9576c65d06a95d","tid":1159169,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1458106_1_20190517204310.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1458106_1_20190517204310.jpg&h=33a3a4d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員胡志偉上星期四在行政長官答問會上，斥責特首林鄭月娥。華員會表示嚴厲讉責，並會與其他公務員團體商討發聯署聲明，要求胡志偉公開道歉，以及要求立法會主席採取懲處措施。<br />\n<br />\n華員會認為，胡志偉言論既是對最高級公職人員的語言暴力，亦是對女性的侮辱，公務人員執行職務期間不應受語言暴力侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n華員會強調會秉持公務員政治中立的原則，行動不是針對政黨或有關修訂《逃犯條例》的爭議。"},{"pid":"a3a0d4ea9b1fba0908bdb9ba05377988a0fba6e5","tid":1159169,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:52:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1458106-20190517.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1458106-20190517.htm&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkJS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=bc04436e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1458106-20190517.htm&h=b03f24f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1458106-20190517.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d0090574d59516c17f3c77b2822c23a31c694db5","tid":1159169,"uid":21545,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:04:33.000Z","msg":"華員會強調會秉持公務員政治中立的原則，行動不是針對政黨或有關修訂《逃犯條例》的爭議。<br />\n此地無銀三百兩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acec1efc706e4483de31824f071e610d341c6b5e","tid":1159169,"uid":249885,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:09:13.000Z","msg":"咩叫華員會？係咪支那駐港間諜組織？"},{"pid":"fd9f